%N A014669 Inverse of 660th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014669 Periodic with period length 660. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 06 2017
%H A014669 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014669/b014669.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014669 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>.
